723
00:30:53.645 --> 00:30:54.501
Mnh-mnh.

724
00:30:54.574 --> 00:30:55.793
He got angry.

725
00:30:55.844 --> 00:30:58.310
mean. isolated.

726
00:30:58.441 --> 00:31:00.884
Every weekend
on hunting trips--

727
00:31:00.959 --> 00:31:02.278
