in the garage.

734
00:31:14.800 --> 00:31:17.668
He had blood on his mouth.
on his clothes.

735
00:31:18.305 --> 00:31:23.240
The Deer Hunter
had been all over the news.

736
00:31:23.765 --> 00:31:26.234
So. in that moment. I knew...

737
00:31:26.353 --> 00:31:28.287
