740
00:31:34.442 --> 00:31:37.114
He knew I knew.
so he couldn't let me go.

741
00:31:37.589 --> 00:31:39.837
And I'd never held a weapon.

742
00:31:40.088 --> 00:31:41.506
I-I-I-I...

743
00:31:42.584 --> 00:31:46.143
I'd fended him off
